00:34:29,370 --> 00:34:30,120
Mẹ?

588
00:34:33,870 --> 00:34:34,750
Mẹ.

589
00:34:36,450 --> 00:34:37,410
Ba.

590
00:34:57,290 --> 00:34:58,080
Yuki!

591
00:35:00,790 --> 00:35:02,450
